post_text:
Lorna Carr, Pleasant Middle School’s head cook, received a SpartanStrong Hero sign today! Lorna has been instrumental in feeding our students during these challenging times. Her staff has prepared over 1,000 meals! Thank you Lorna! #spartanstronghero ⁦
@JenniferAdams65
